Package edu.uml.cs.isense.sync

Class Summary
SyncTime Allows the user to share his device's current time with other devices on the same network.
TimeFailed Asks the user to retry when the socket fails to receive a time packet.
TimeReceived Tells the user what time was received and what its offset is from local time.
TimeReset Tells the user that their time offset has been reset back to zero.
